data.description: Looking for a turn key retreat? This 4 bedroom, 3 bath home on over 5 acres fits the description. Lovingly and meticulously cared for this flowing center hall colonial with eat in kitchen with granite countertops, family room with wood burning fireplace, formal dining room and master ensuite is set on a lovely picturesque road in Sullivan County. A 2 car garage and a basement just waiting to be finished completes the lower level. Sliding glass doors lead from the kitchen to a beautiful deck. The basement has sliding glass doors that lead to a shady, long patio. Enjoy nature with the charming chicken coup and potagers garden where thyme, basil, rosemary, blueberries, and raspberries grow close to the house for garden to table dining. You'll love this house!
